---
import qr_line from "../../assets/qrs/qr_line.jpg";
import qr_sns from "../../assets/qrs/qr_sns.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---
<section id="contact" class="section">
    <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-section">
        <div class="contact-text">
        <h2>JOIN US!</h2>
        <p>
            新歓期間はモデルロケット製作や電子工作を体験できます！興味があれば学年・学部問わず大歓迎！日程は各種SNSやオープンチャットでチェック！
        </p>
        <p
            style="
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: $gray-light);
            margin-top: 20px;
            "
        >
            QR画像をタップしてリンク先にジャンプできます
        </p>
        </div>
        <div class="qr-grid">
        <div class="qr-item">
            <span class="qr-label">新歓オープンチャット</span>
            <a
            href="https://line.me/ti/g2/s53-cMOZ_WM-weZjBFGe9BK26XzErD270IH3ZA?utm_source=invitation&utm_medium=link_copy&utm_campaign=default"
            class="qr-img"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
            <Image
                src={qr_line}
                alt="LINE_QR"
                style="cursor: pointer"
                format="webp"
                quality={70}
            />
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="qr-item">
            <span class="qr-label">各種SNSリンク</span>
            <a
            href="https://qr.quel.jp/om/b0orrd"
            class="qr-img"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
                <Image
                    src={qr_sns}
                    alt="LINE_SNS"
                    style="cursor: pointer"
                    format="webp"
                    quality={70}
                />
            </a>
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
</section>  
<style lang="scss">
.contact-section {
    background: $dark;
    border-radius: $radius-lg;
    padding: 60px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
    .contact-section {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    padding: 40px 24px;
    }
}

.contact-text h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.contact-text p {
    color: $gray-light;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.qr-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 30px;
}

.qr-item {
    text-align: center;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: $radius;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
}

.qr-img {
    width: 140px;
    height: 140px;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    background: white;
    padding: 8px;
    border-radius: $radius-sm;
}

.qr-label {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: block;
}

</style>